WEBVTT

00:02.274 --> 00:06.874
<font color=#5484A4>-==MMMM®==-</font>

00:07.546 --> 00:11.229
V.T.R. No 7226 THE DEVIL OF CHRISTMAS
Part one, take one.

00:11.412 --> 00:13.633
In five, four, three...

00:15.000 --> 00:21.074
